# Real-Time Fraud Detection API

This project implements a **real-time fraud detection system** using a trained **LightGBM classifier**, exposed through a **FastAPI REST API**.  
The API accepts transaction features as input and returns fraud probability and prediction based on a custom decision threshold.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

- Binary classification problem (fraud vs non-fraud)
- Handles highly imbalanced transaction data
- Optimized for recall using probability-based thresholding
- Designed as a production-style ML inference service

---

## ğŸ“Š Model Performance

- **Recall:** 0.85  
- **Precision:** 0.78  

The model prioritizes detecting fraudulent transactions while maintaining a reasonable false-positive rate.

---

## ğŸ§  Tech Stack

- **Language:** Python  
- **ML Model:** LightGBM (LGBMClassifier)  
- **API Framework:** FastAPI  
- **Model Serialization:** joblib  
- **Data Handling:** NumPy, Pandas  
- **Deployment Ready:** Docker / Cloud compatible  

